.png","167959","此文提供在 Mac OS X 上透過 Yahoo! 奇摩輸入法使用快倉六的方法。","/scj6-mac-yahoo-keykey",{"articles_id":116,"__typename":18},{"id":117,"title":118,"cover_image":119,"summary":124,"slug":125,"__typename":19},"75407dcc-c619-432b-bb5b-21bd10bdbbfd","macOS 快倉六",{"id":120,"folder":9,"filename_disk":121,"filename_download":122,"type":86,"description":9,"filesize":123,"__typename":88},"fead2ca8-c3bc-41ae-a4a2-12527e40df08","fead2ca8-c3bc-41ae-a4a2-12527e40df08.png","Mac-scj6-cin-3.png","55633","繼先前本站文章講述如何透過 Yahoo! 奇摩輸入法使用快倉六後，筆者發現 Mac OS X 10.5 及 10.6 系統本身可以製作自己的輸入法（類似微軟視窗之通用輸入法）。","/scj6-macos",{"articles_id":127,"__typename":18},{"id":128,"title":129,"cover_image":130,"summary":135,"slug":136,"__typename":19},"a1a783bc-7f41-4df1-8284-14b7969a0199","在 MeeGo 使用快倉六",{"id":131,"folder":9,"filename_disk":132,"filename_download":133,"type":86,"description":9,"filesize":134,"__typename":88},"a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf","a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf.png","MeeGo-Screenshot-1.png","62490","本文講述如何在 MeeGo 1.0 for Netbooks 安裝及使用快速倉頡第六代中文輸入法。","/scj6-meego",{"articles_id":138,"__typename":18},{"id":139,"title":140,"cover_image":141,"summary":146,"slug":147,"__typename":19},"7fa853ed-8edc-402e-b34e-402e1fad1585","用於 Nokia N900 maemo 之快倉六",{"id":142,"folder":9,"filename_disk":143,"filename_download":144,"type":86,"description":9,"filesize":145,"__typename":88},"3e1f08e4-6982-4d49-99ae-fd3405731d8c","3e1f08e4-6982-4d49-99ae-fd3405731d8c.png","maemo-scj6.png","1059730","用於 maemo mscim 之快倉六軟件","/scj6-maemo",{"articles_id":149,"__typename":18},{"id":150,"title":151,"cover_image":9,"summary":9,"slug":152,"__typename":19},"b0badc5e-272e-463f-ba01-59aad7d15d13","相關網站","/related-links",{"articles_id":154,"__typename":18},{"id":155,"title":156,"cover_image":9,"summary":157,"slug":59,"__typename":19},"16f388f4-5324-4377-80a3-e8ddd8995875","快速倉頡輸入法第六代","快速倉頡輸入法第六代（快倉六）是一個多功能和多任務的輸入法系統。在功能方面，它不但擁有多種不同版本的倉頡輸入法、速成輸入法、廣東話輸入法、高效率的標點、特殊符號和數字編碼、日文編碼、香港政府三千常用字編碼、簡碼和容錯碼。",{"downloadlink":159},